Fidelity Bank Plc wishes to announce new Board appointments to replace the retired and outgoing Non-Executive Directors, the Board is pleased to announce the appointment of three Non-Executive Directors.  Mrs. Amaka Theodora Onwughalu Mr. Nelson Chidozie Nweke Mr. Chinedu Eric Okeke The appointments of Mrs. Onwughalu and Mr. Nweke have been approved by the Central Bank of Nigeria (CBN) whilst that of Mr. Okeke is awaiting CBN approval.